## Checklist for Step 3

- [ ] Validator service created
- [ ] Validator has all 3 methods (create/update/delete)
- [ ] Validator **never throws** - returns errors array
- [ ] Validator **never mutates** entity maps
- [ ] Validator contains only business logic validation
- [ ] Builder service created
- [ ] Builder extends `WorkspaceEntityMigrationBuilderService`
- [ ] Builder delegates to validator
- [ ] Builder creates actions with universal entities
- [ ] ⚠️ **Builder imported in orchestrator**
- [ ] ⚠️ **Builder injected in orchestrator constructor**
- [ ] ⚠️ **Builder called in `buildWorkspaceMigration` method**
- [ ] ⚠️ **Actions added to orchestrator return statement**

**Missing orchestrator wiring is the #1 reason entities don't work!**

